room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by EscapeIQ in Los Angeles
room_address: 1135 E. 5th St. Suite 8 Los Angeles, CA 90013
room_description: Secret Agent IQ has been captured! Intel suggests he is being held captive deep inside a vault in the Arts District of downtown LA. Luckily, Agent IQ managed to leave some clues leading to his exact location. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to break into the vault and escape with Agent IQ. You’ll have to hurry, though — there’s only a 60-minute window for the rescue! Good Luck!
